    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 5.8000001033
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "（大変、大変、もうこんな時間！ 早く準備しないと……）\n（んぎゃぁっ、ヘアアイロンのコードが足に！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8000001033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.966666325
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.966666325
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "（朝からこころちゃんの部屋がやけに騒がしいな……）\n（ドタバタしてるけど、一体何をしてるんだろう？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 21.1999999126
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 21.1999999126
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "（あー、忙しい忙しい忙しいっっっ！）\n（なんで十二月六日ってたった二十四時間しかないの！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.9218060574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 28.8666667702
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "（スーパーアイドルこころのお誕生日なんだから百時間は）\n（ないとみんながこころのことお祝い出来ないじゃん！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "（はーあ、今日は世界中のこころ推しの人達が）\n（思う存分こころのことをお祝い出来ますように！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5266.666666699997,
          "startTime": 46.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.0833316567
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_garden-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 46.0833316567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "（部屋から出て行くこころちゃんが気になって）\n（付いて来てみたけど……あの荷物、何をする気！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "（よし、準備も出来たし誕生日の儀、開催じゃー！）\n（こころが沢山の人に祝福されることを願い――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.9666643779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "（赤崎こころをーーーーーーーーーー！！）\n（祝いたまへーーーーーーーーーー！！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "（お頼みもうすー！　お頼みもうすー！）\n（ほんにゃらほんにゃらズンドコズンドコ！！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.9662526772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "赤崎こころを祝いたまへーーーー皆の衆ーーーーー！！\nお頼みもうすー！　ほんにゃら誕生日！　本日誕生日！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.2333216351,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5633.345031600001,
          "startTime": 87.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こころちゃーん……お、おはよ～\n早朝からダンス……？　の練習……かな？　偉いね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.1999923707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "な、渚ちゃん！？　えっと……そ、そうです！　これは\n本日収録の『いちばんカワイイTV』の練習でして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "けして誕生日だからって浮かれた訳ではないですから！\n勘違いしないで下さいよ！　番組のっ！　練習ですっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1669615035,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9266.363691799996,
          "startTime": 122.4333251953
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、お誕生日ってなんだかそわそわしちゃうよね\nはい、これ私からこころちゃんへのお誕生日プレゼント",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.899991862,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4666.6538005,
          "startTime": 127.5666456625
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "だから別にそわそわとかは……ありがとうございます\nはっ！？　これは最近話題の『プルプリ桃プリン』！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.1333251953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "プリンであり桃、桃でありプリンという二面性を持ち\n全国のプリン＆桃好きを唸らせた一品ではないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.4333251953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "（こころちゃん、自分からみんなにお祝いしてって言いに）\n（行きそうなのに意外と祝われ待ちなのかも……なんて！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.3333251953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、このプリン、プルプリしててホント可愛い……\n渚ちゃん、何こころのこと見てニヤニヤしてるんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.7333251953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、お面借りていい？　私もこころちゃんの誕生日が\n素敵な一日になることを願ってさっきの踊りしたいな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.3333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_01-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "うう……やっぱり見られてたんですね……\nはぁ……仕方ないですね。じゃあ、やりますか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.3666585286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "赤崎こころをーーー！　祝いたまへーーーー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.1999962891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ほんにゃら、ほんにゃら、本日誕生日！　本日誕生日！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.7999983237,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}